    public static interface Classes.Streaming
extends Function<Class<?>,Stream<Class<?>>>
    Provides streaming methods from Classes as predefined Functions.

    • Field Detail

      • SUPER_CLASS

        static final Classes.Streaming SUPER_CLASS
        For the sake of completeness and convenience: a Function to treat the direct superclass of a given Class as a Stream.

        The result will be an empty Stream if the given Class has no superclass. Otherwise the result is a Stream consisting of exactly one element, namely the requested superclass.
